OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FA retired Police Superintendent has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed for six years after a
OL,8,Fjudge heard how he broke into his ex-
OL,9,Fwife's home and planned to attack her
OL,10,Fas part of a suicide plan.
OL,12,FEx-Metropolitan Police chief Martyn
OL,13,FHorne smashed through the door of the
OL,14,Ffamily home on October 16 2023, with
OL,15,Fthe intention of seriously harming his
OL,16,Fformer wife.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/15
