OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FThe 73-year-old, from Drayton
OL,7,FBeauchamp near Aylesbury, Bucks,
OL,8,Fparked his car at a reservoir and then
OL,9,Fwalked to the house before hiding in a
OL,10,Fgarden shed until the morning.
OL,12,FDuring extensive doorbell footage
OL,13,Fshown in court, Horne was seen banging
OL,14,Fon the front door, before smashing his
OL,15,Fway through it and forcing his way
OL,16,Finto the property.
OL,18,FHis former wife immediately fled to a
OL,19,Fneighbour's property seeking safety.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
