OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FA judge heard that during a 999 call
OL,7,Fshe made, Ms Sharon Heyes was heard to
OL,8,Fsay repeatedly: "He's going to kill
OL,9,Fme."
OL,11,FHorne, who had reached the Police
OL,12,FSuperintendent rank before retiring,
OL,13,Fcut tape and stuck it to his top for
OL,14,Feasy peeling and cut rope to a certain
OL,15,Flength - to restrain and detain Ms
OL,16,FHeyes, the judge said during the
OL,17,Fsentencing hearing at Reading Crown
OL,18,FCourt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/15
