OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FThe court heard that a B&Q receipt
OL,7,Ffrom the day previous, detailed
OL,8,FHorne's purchases of Gorilla Tape, a
OL,9,Ffolding knife with five blades and
OL,10,Ffive metres of braided rope.
OL,12,FMs Heyes, who read her victim impact
OL,13,Fstatements from the public gallery of
OL,14,Fthe court, said the incidents had
OL,15,F"turned her world upside down." She
OL,16,Fhas since moved from the property
OL,17,Fwhere the burglary happened, the court
OL,18,Fheard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
