OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FThe victim, a former police officer
OL,7,Fand senior staff nurse, received
OL,8,Fseveral commendations during her time
OL,9,Fwith the Metropolitan Police. These
OL,10,Fincluded climbing under a train to
OL,11,Fassist a suicidal woman on the track
OL,12,Fand talking down an armed offender.
OL,14,FMs Heyes said she had faced aggression
OL,15,Fthroughout her career but never
OL,16,Fimagined she would face aggression in
OL,17,Fthe sanctuary of her own home.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
