OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,F"I cannot lose the image of him hiding
OL,7,Fin the garden. The look of his face
OL,8,Fimprinted in my mind," she told the
OL,9,Fjudge.
OL,11,FMs Heyes said she had become obsessive
OL,12,Fabout locking doors and was constantly
OL,13,Fchecking wardrobes and rooms in her
OL,14,Fhouse.
OL,16,FShe has been unable to revalidate her
OL,17,FNMC nursing licence due to her ongoing
OL,18,Fsickness with depression and anxiety
OL,19,Fas a result of Horne's actions, the
OL,20,Fcourt heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/15
