OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FJudge Neil Millard told Ms Heyes: "If
OL,7,Fyou take anything from today, take
OL,8,Ffrom this hearing that it takes
OL,9,Fstrength to go through the
OL,10,Fproceedings, it takes strength to
OL,11,Fstand and read those statements in
OL,12,Ffront of others.
OL,14,F"Remember the strength it took to get
OL,15,Fyou here today and I hope you can get
OL,16,Fback to some measure of the person who
OL,17,Fwas so full of confidence and joy for
OL,18,Flife not too many years ago."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
