OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FMartyn Hynes, defending Horne, said:
OL,7,FThis case is incredibly sad and
OL,8,Finvolves two former police officers
OL,9,Fwho had achieved great success in
OL,10,Ftheir careers and had a happy and
OL,11,Fperhaps exciting time ahead of them
OL,12,Fboth."
OL,14,FMr Hynes said the relationship became
OL,15,Frelatively volatile and later broke
OL,16,Fdown.
OL,18,FThe judge said Horne "plainly intended
OL,19,Fto cause her (the victim) serious
OL,20,Fharm."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
