OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FAt the time of the burglary, Horne was
OL,7,Fon bail for two other incidents which
OL,8,Fhad happened earlier in 2023.
OL,10,FOn July 31 2023, Horne slammed the
OL,11,Fvictim's phone into her left leg as
OL,12,Fshe was planning to drive him to John
OL,13,FRadcliffe Hospital, because she could
OL,14,Fnot work out how to use the car sat-
OL,15,Fnav, a statement from the victim said.
OL,17,FOn September 11 2023, Horne pinned Ms
OL,18,FHeyes to the ground and tried to
OL,19,Fsuffocate her with a sock and a pillow.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
