OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FJudge Millard said: "This case is
OL,7,Fplainly a tragedy for all involved. I
OL,8,Fcannot avoid noting these offences did
OL,9,Fnot occur suddenly.
OL,11,F"In the heat of moment, had you got
OL,12,Fhold of her, it is impossible for me
OL,13,Fto say how serious the level of harm
OL,14,Fshe would have come to would have
OL,15,Fbeen."
OL,17,FAfter breaking into the property,
OL,18,FHorne went to the bathroom and cut his
OL,19,Fwrists, the judge heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
