OL,3,CRetired police chief who plotted to
OL,4,Cattack ex-wife jailed for 6 years
OL,6,FHe said that he had no doubts Horne's
OL,7,Fintention was to end his own life but
OL,8,Fhe also intended to cause Ms Heyes
OL,9,Freally serious harm.
OL,11,FFor one count of assault by beating,
OL,12,Fassault occasioning actual bodily
OL,13,Fharm, intentional suffocation and
OL,14,Fburglary with the intent to commit
OL,15,Fgrievous bodily harm, Horne was jailed
OL,16,Ffor six years.
OL,18,FHe was convicted of the burglary
OL,19,Fmatter at trial. He had also indicated
OL,20,Fguilty pleas to the other matters.
